\large \omega(n)=\sum_{p\in\mathbb{P}}\;\sum_{r=1}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{p^{r+1}}}\sum_{j=1}^{p-1}{\;\;\;\sum_{k=0}^{\;p^{r+1}-1}\cos\left\lbrace 2k\pi \left(\frac{n+(p-j)p^{r}}{p^{r+1}}\right)\right\rbrace}
